code: public static String apply(String value) {     try {         return URLDecoder.decode(value, "UTF-8").     } catch (UnsupportedEncodingException e) {         throw new IllegalArgumentException("Could not URL-decode value.", e).     } }
@Override protected String process(String value) {     return apply(value). }

@Override protected URLDecodeProcessor newProcessor(String tag, Map<String, Object> config, String field, boolean ignoreMissing, String targetField) {     return new URLDecodeProcessor(tag, field, ignoreMissing, targetField). }
